Introduction to Dark Mode

Gusanos 0.9 has lights, but to utilize them, you must activate dark mode. To do this, you must hit ~ to activate the console; then type in vid_dark_mode 1 (0 to deactivate). Note that dark mode will likely eventually be map and mod specific; if the map and mod you're playing don't implement lights, you will likely be shrouded in…</description>
